.DT
query_amount
Discworld cont_medium help
query_amount

Name
.SI 5
query_amount - The amount of this stuff.
.EI

Syntax
.SI 5
int query_amount();
.EI

Description
.SP 5 5
Returns the amount of the stuff in question.  This is the number of
things of the continuous medium.

Eg: If you had 20 marbles and marbles were handled as a continuous
medium, this would return 20.
.EP

See also
.SP 5 5
set_amount, set_weight_unit, adjust_amount, pile_size, amount_size,
query_weight_unit
.EP
